8
Be the Single-threaded leader who owns significant complex problems and organizational goals to improve Returns Experience around shopping and fulfillment
Define the short-term and long-term vision for the area, leveraging data, insights, benchmarking, and other associated information for decision making.
Evangelize this opportunity to generate support; builds business cases for senior leadership review towards awareness, interest and investment in the problem space.
Break down ambitions into SMART goals that make a material contribution towards the ambition
Influence stakeholders and Amazon team to partner on planning, organizing and executing initiatives towards the goals.
Ruthlessly prioritize to drive the biggest customer impact; balances short-term challenges and long-term benefits.
Confidently operate in a highly ambiguous space; simplifies decision-making using a combination of data, anecdotes, insights, and escalations
Regularly communicate to very senior leadership to inform on status, progress, challenges, blockers, and support asks on critical organizational goals.
